#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Hex Outlaw variant with a moving obstacle. A stagecoach bounces vertically through the center of the arena, blocking bullets with unpredictable timing. Time your shots for the gaps. The stagecoach adds a rhythm-based element to the classic duel."
msgstr "이동 장애가있는 Hex Outlaw 변형. 단계별 반송은 평등한 타이밍을 가진 탄알을 막는 경기장의 센터를 통해서 수직으로 반송합니다. 틈에 대한 샷을 시간. stagecoach는 고전적인 duel에 리듬 기반 요소를 추가합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Hex Outlaw variant with bouncing bullets. A wide wall blocks direct horizontal shots — fire at 30-degree angles and bounce bullets off the ceiling or floor to hit your opponent. This variant rewards geometric thinking and precise vertical positioning."
msgstr "Hex Outlaw 변종을 끓는 총알. 넓은 벽 블록 직접 수평 샷 - 30도 각도에서 화재 및 천장 또는 바닥에서 상대를 명중합니다. 이 변형 보상 기하학적 사고 및 정확한 수직 포지셔닝."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Hex Outlaw variant with no obstacles and full horizontal movement. Each gunslinger can advance within their 30% of the arena — closing the distance reduces your opponent's reaction time but leaves you exposed too. The purest test of reflexes and positioning."
