msgstr "— 8 방향 이동"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move left/right"
msgstr "- 왼쪽 이동/right"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move left/right on blocks or shore"
msgstr "- 왼쪽 이동/right 블록 또는 해안에"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_block_breakers.html.heex:13
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_pong.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move paddle"
msgstr "— 패들 이동"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move player"
msgstr "- 플레이어 이동"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_warlords.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move shield vertically"
msgstr "- 수직으로 이동 방패"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:13
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Move vertically and set aim direction (last pressed determines angle)"
msgstr "— 수직으로 이동하고 목표 방향 (마지막 눌러 각도를 결정)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Neutral. Step on it to claim it (+1 igloo piece)"
msgstr "- 중립. 그것을 주장하는 단계 (+1 igloo 조각)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No avalanche, no items, pure time trial racing"
msgstr "— 아니 avalanche, 아니 항목, 순수한 시간 시험 경주"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:110
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:203
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No block stealing, pure construction race"
msgstr "— 훔치는 구획 없음, 순수한 건축 인종"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No fuel means no reason to brake unless you're about to crash. Keep the pedal down."
msgstr "- 연료가 충돌하지 않는 경우 브레이크에 아무 이유도 없습니다. 아래 페달을 유지하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:59
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:163
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No mines, pure skill competition"
msgstr "- 광산 없음, 순수한 기술 경쟁"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No obstacle, but players can advance horizontally within their half"
msgstr "- 장애물 없음, 그러나 플레이어는 절반 안에 수평으로 전진 할 수 있습니다"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:117
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— No timer, first to 5 goals, puck speeds up with each goal"
msgstr "— 타이머 없음, 첫 번째 5 목표, 각 목표와 속도"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:48
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Not all ice rows are equal. Focus on rows with predictable patterns first."
msgstr "— 모든 얼음 줄은 동일하지 않습니다. 예측 가능한 패턴을 가진 행에 집중하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:66
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— One bullet at a time. A wasted shot on the stagecoach gives your opponent a free window to reposition."
msgstr "— 한 번에 총알. stagecoach에 대한 wasted 샷은 상대에게 무료 창을 재구성합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:86
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Open/close on blocks. Open = dangerous, closed = safe (from round 4)"
msgstr "— 오픈/close 블록에. = 위험하다, 닫히는 = 안전 (둥근에서 4)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Patrols the shore. Dodge to reach your igloo!"
msgstr "— 해안을 순찰합니다. 당신의 igloo에 도달하는 Dodge!"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Perfect your jump timing between rows to minimize time between block collections."
msgstr "- 블록 수집 사이에 시간을 최소화하기 위해 행간에 점프 타이밍을 완벽하게합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Puck reflects off top/bottom walls"
msgstr "— Puck는 상단에 반영/bottom 벽 벽"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_boxing.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Punch (alternates left/right arm automatically)"
msgstr "— 펀치 (왼쪽에/right 팔 자동)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:74
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Ride the ice blocks (from round 2)"
msgstr "— 얼음 블록을 타고 (둥근에서 2)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:51
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Risky shots that go out cost you a whole game. Consistency beats flash in Sudden Death."
msgstr "— 위험한 샷은 전체 게임을 비용. 일관성은 스도덴 죽음에서 플래시를 이깁니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_night.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Save your turbo boost for fog-free moments when you can actually see the road."
msgstr "— 당신이 실제로 도로를 볼 수 있을 때 fog 자유로운 순간을 위한 당신의 터보 후원을 저장하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Scarce fuel means every depot matters. Plan your path to hit fuel depots even if it means fewer enemy kills."
msgstr "— Scarce 연료는 모든 depot 사정을 의미합니다. 적은 적의 사망을 의미하는 경우에도 연료를 저해하는 길을 계획하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Serve (during serving phase)"
msgstr "— Serve (제공 단계)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Server alternates after every point. Know when you're serving to maximize advantage."
msgstr "- 각 지점 후 서버 교체. 장점을 극대화 할 때 알고 있습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Shared screen, no alien drops, fight together"
msgstr "— 공유 화면, 외계인 방울, 함께 싸울"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Sharp turns slow you down. Plan your path 2-3 obstacles ahead for the smoothest line."
msgstr "- 샤프가 느립니다. 가장 매끄러운 선을 위해 2-3의 장애물을 미리 계획하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:17
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:17
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Shoot in your facing direction"
msgstr "— 당신의 얼굴 방향에서 촬영"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Slow down for dense enemy clusters to maximize hits. Speed up in empty stretches to save fuel."
msgstr "- dense 적 클러스터를 위해 아래로 느립니다. 연료를 절약하기 위해 빈 기지에서 가속화하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:54
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Sparse obstacles, slow avalanche, wide gates"
msgstr "— Sparse 장애물, 느린 avalanche, 넓은 문"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:50
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Speed boosts keep you ahead of the avalanche. Missing one could be fatal later."
msgstr "— 속도 향상은 avalanche의 앞서 유지. 미스링은 나중에 지방이 될 수 있습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Standard 60% success rate. Don't commit to a tackle unless you're sure you're close enough."
msgstr "— 표준 60% 성공률. 당신이 충분히 가까운지 확실하지 않는 한 촉촉한에 투입하지 마십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Standing near the ceiling or floor gives your bullets a shorter bounce path, making them harder to dodge."
msgstr "- 천장 또는 바닥 근처의 서는 더 짧은 반송 경로를 제공합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Steer jet laterally"
msgstr "— Steer 제트는 나중에"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:11
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Steer left/right"
msgstr "— Steer 왼쪽/right"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Step on your own block to undo it (-1 piece)"
msgstr "— 자신의 블록에서 undo (-1 조각)에 단계"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Step to steal it! You +1 piece, they -1 piece (2-piece swing!)"
msgstr "— 그것을 훔치는 단계! 당신은 +1 조각, 그들은 -1 조각 (2 조각 스윙!)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Stepping on your opponent's blocks steals them. Use it offensively when you're ahead."
msgstr "— 상대의 블록에 대한 단계는 그들을 훔칩니다. 당신이 앞서 있을 때 그것을 공격적으로 사용합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:23
#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:23
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Tackle opponent to steal puck"
msgstr "- 훔치는 상대"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The 25% speed boost makes long-range shots more effective. Catch the opponent off guard."
msgstr "— 25% 속도 향상은 더 효과적인 장거리 샷을 만듭니다. 상대를 감시합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The 80% success rate means tackling is almost always worth it. Chase the puck carrier relentlessly."
msgstr "- 80 %의 성공률은 압착이 거의 항상 가치가 있음을 의미합니다. puck 캐리어를 relentlessly 차."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:60
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The ball angle depends on where it hits your player. Position yourself to control shot direction."
msgstr "— 공 각은 플레이어를 조회하는 곳에 달려 있습니다. 샷 방향을 제어 할 수 있습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_escape.html.heex:43
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The center of the course gives you the most options to dodge left or right as obstacles appear."
msgstr "— 과정의 중심은 장애물이 나타나는 것처럼 왼쪽 또는 오른쪽으로 가장 옵션을 제공합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The first few goals are at normal puck speed. Build a lead before the puck becomes a missile."
msgstr "— 첫번째 몇몇 목표는 정상 puck 속도에 있습니다. puck이 미사일이되기 전에 리드를 구축하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The stagecoach bounces at a constant speed. Count the timing and fire during the gap windows."
msgstr "— 연속 속도에서 stagecoach bounces. 갭 창에서 타이밍과 화재를 계산합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_stagecoach.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— The stagecoach spends the least time at the top and bottom of its bounce, creating wider shooting windows."
msgstr "— stagecoach는 더 넓은 촬영 창을 만드는 도약의 상단과 하단에 적어도 시간을 보냅니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_skiing_clean.html.heex:52
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Tight gaps require micro-adjustments. Don't overcorrect and bounce between obstacles."
msgstr "— 단단한 간격은 micro-adjustments를 요구합니다. 장애물 사이에 과도하고 반송하지 마십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:59
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Touching the riverbank kills you instantly. Stay centered when the river narrows."
msgstr "— Riverbank가 즉시 죽일 때. 강이 좁을 때 중심을 유지하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Walk into the free puck to pick it up automatically"
msgstr "— 무료 puck로 걸어가 자동으로 픽업"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:65
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Weave through tight gaps between AI cars. Each overtake counts — even risky ones."
msgstr "- AI 자동차 간의 꽉 격차를 통해 직물. 각 섭취량 — 위험도."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:62
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— When the puck is fast, stay between the puck and your goal. Reaction time shrinks."
msgstr "— puck이 빠르면 puck과 목표 사이에 머물 수 있습니다. 반응 시간 수축."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_blizzard.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With 60° on the clock, you have time. Don't rush jumps and fall into the water."
msgstr "— 시계에 60°로, 당신은 시간이 있습니다. 물로 떨어지지 마십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:55
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With 80% tackle success, holding the puck is dangerous. Shoot on sight."
msgstr "— 80% 촉촉한 성공으로, puck를 들고 위험합니다. 촬영 시력."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:43
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With a 3-second cooldown, you can drop mines much more frequently. Use them to disrupt your opponent's rhythm."
msgstr "— 3-second cooldown으로, 당신은 더 자주 광산을 떨어질 수 있습니다. 상대의 리듬을 파괴하기 위해 그들을 사용합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_enduro_sprint.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With clear visibility, use turbo when the road ahead is clear for maximum overtakes."
msgstr "- 명확한 가시성으로, 도로가 앞선다면 터보를 사용합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_invaders_blitz.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With lowered combo thresholds (2 kills for a drop), rapid-fire is your best weapon against the opponent."
msgstr "— 더 낮은 콤보 임계 값 (2 드롭 살인), 급속 화재는 상대에 대한 최고의 무기입니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_nml.html.heex:57
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With no obstacles, vertical movement is your only defense. Never stand still."
msgstr "- 장애물 없음, 수직 운동은 유일한 방어입니다. 아직도 서."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_sudden.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With one-point games, an ace or unreturnable serve is an instant game win."
msgstr "— One-point 게임으로, 에이스 또는 무수한 봉사는 즉시 게임 승리입니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_tennis_quick.html.heex:39
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With only 3 games needed, losing even one game puts you at a serious disadvantage."
msgstr "- 필요한 유일한 3 게임, 심지어 하나의 게임을 잃은 것은 심각한 단점에 당신을 넣어."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_blitz.html.heex:64
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— With only 5 sections, maximizing points per section is key. Prioritize high-value targets."
msgstr "— 단 5개의 단면도로, 단면도 당 최대화점은 열쇠입니다. 높은 가치 목표를 우선 순위."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_frost_peaceful.html.heex:41
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Without block stealing, the fastest path through the ice rows wins. Plan your circuit."
msgstr "— 차단 없이, 얼음 줄을 통해서 가장 빠른 경로 승리. 회로를 계획하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_raid_pacifist.html.heex:45
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Without mines to worry about, you can fly more aggressively. But don't forget to refuel — fuel depots are your lifeline."
msgstr "—에 대해 걱정하지 않고, 더 공격적으로 비행 할 수 있습니다. 그러나 급유를 잊지 마세요 - 연료 저장소는 당신의 생명입니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:72
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— You can only fire one bullet at a time. Don't waste shots — wait for a clear angle."
msgstr "- 한 번에 한 번의 총알을 불릴 수 있습니다. 폐기물 샷을 낭비하지 마십시오 - 명확한 각도를 기다립니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_outlaw_ricochet.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— Your last directional input sets your aim. Keep moving up and down to make your shots unpredictable."
msgstr "— 당신의 마지막 방향 입력은 당신의 목표를 놓습니다. 당신의 샷을 예측할 수 있도록 이동하고 아래로 유지하십시오."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_blitz.html.heex:44
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— more aggressive, less risk"
msgstr "— 더 공격적인, 더 적은 위험"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:32
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— play until someone reaches 5 goals"
msgstr "— 누군가가 5 목표 도달 때까지 플레이"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey_showdown.html.heex:38
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— puck gets faster with each goal scored"
msgstr "— puck는 각 목표 점수로 더 빠르게 얻습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:68
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— puck is freed at opponent's position"
msgstr "— puck는 상대의 위치에 자유롭습니다"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_hex_hockey.html.heex:74
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "— you are stunned for 300ms (can't move or act)"
msgstr "— 당신은 300ms를 위해 기절됩니다 (움직일 수 없습니다 또는 행위)"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_single_session.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ". Only one browser window or tab can be connected with the same nickname at a time."
msgstr ". 1개의 브라우저 창 또는 탭만 동시에 동일한 별명과 연결될 수 있습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_p2p_games.html.heex:8
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "/game <nickname>"
msgstr "/game <nickname>"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_star_duel.html.heex:69
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "2 seconds of invulnerability after each respawn"
msgstr "각 respawn 후에 취약점의 2 초"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_block_breakers.html.heex:19
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "3 shared lives — if the ball exits top or bottom, both players lose a life"
msgstr "3 공유 생활 — 공이 정상 또는 바닥을 종료하면 두 플레이어는 인생을 잃습니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_block_breakers.html.heex:25
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "50 blocks arranged in 5 rows of 10 with different point values"
msgstr "5개의 줄에서 배열되는 50의 구획 다른 점 가치로 10"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_debris_field.html.heex:40
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "8 asteroids of varying sizes are scattered across the arena"
msgstr "다재다능한 크기의 8개의 소행성은 경기장의 맞은편에 흩어져 있습니다"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_block_breakers.html.heex:13
